bio: <p>Denis Jacquerye is involved in language technology, software \
  localization and font engineering. He's been the co-lead of the DejaVu \
  Font project for a few years and is working with the African Network \
  for Localization (ANLoc) to remove language limitations that exist \
  in today's technology. Denis currently lives in Brussels.</p>
